            <h2 class="text-center ">Tarot</h2>
            <p class="text-justify">
                Palmistry, or palm reading, is an ancient art that unveils the secrets of one's character and future through the lines and shapes found in the palms of the hands. As a profound and captivating practice, palmistry, also known as chiromancy, delves into the unique patterns of the palm to offer insights into a person's life journey, traits, and destiny.
            </p>
            <p class="text-justify">
                At its core, palmistry revolves around the interpretation of the lines, mounts, and shapes on the palm. These elements are believed to reveal various aspects of an individual's personality and future. For instance, the heart line, head line, and life line are three primary lines examined in palmistry. Each line serves as a map to different areas of one’s life:
            </p>
            <p class="text-justify">
