                <strong>The Life Line:</strong> Often misconceived as a predictor of lifespan, the life line actually represents overall health, vitality, and the general course of one's life.
            </p>
            <p class="text-justify">
                In addition to these lines, palmists also study the mounts—elevated areas of flesh at the base of each finger. These mounts, named after celestial bodies like the Mount of Venus and the Mount of Jupiter, offer further clues about an individual’s characteristics and potential.
            </p>


